        History
        -------
        
        0.4.0 (2015-08-08)
        ---------------------
        
        * Added support for text input areas.
        
        0.3.1 (2015-05-08)
        ---------------------
        
        * Slight unifications to the way you register behaviors.
        
        0.3.0 (2015-05-08)
        ---------------------
        
        * Event loop and binding listeners.
        
        0.2.0 (2015-04-26)
        ---------------------
        
        * Rendering text into boxes.
        
        0.1.0 (2015-04-25)
        ---------------------
        
        * First release on PyPI.
        
